<Layout title="Directions">
    <section>
      <h1>Directions for Geekcamp 2024</h1>
      Geekcamp 2024 is at <b>SMU Connexion, Level 5</b>. 
      <h3>
        1. City Hall (Exit A) - step-free access
      </h3>
      <p>
        Get up to street level via Exit A. You can take the escalator or a lift. Exit Raffles City by the door on the left side. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449085319123015/IMG_5602.jpg?ex=6750d508&is=674f8388&hm=de918a8951a0c3da7c0f8e8da5d08355a906124cd9b7adc315421f7f2dfb35d8&=&format=webp"/>
        You should see Coffee Bean and Tea Leaf  and a large white gift box in the distance. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449085860315217/IMG_5600.jpg?ex=6750d508&is=674f8388&hm=3cd4489565ab1f772b0ec8efc97df2565e7936b576c2633ae5d6af1c631a6c5c&=&format=webp"/>
        Go towards the gift box. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449086548054066/IMG_5599.jpg?ex=6750d508&is=674f8388&hm=1bfdfa564575dfefa62ac6e320297f390ef4f83f6973c51fd0450331ca76b15e&=&format=webp&width=1518&height=1138"/>
        There's a traffic light behind the gift box - cross the road here. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449087319801896/IMG_5598.jpg?ex=6750d509&is=674f8389&hm=a9a4e1933407cd0d0d668c378ba38325c5c9a9027b1dbb7f926bf0e8ee93f478&=&format=webp&width=1518&height=1138"/>
        Go down this road all the way till you reach SMU. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449087898746931/IMG_5595.jpg?ex=6750d509&is=674f8389&hm=1179e3a8aea845d1b7ee373cfd75719aec69dfda4cc205303aca61f29e93f176&=&format=webp&width=1518&height=1138"/>
        When you reach SMU Connexion, you should see a I ❤️ SMU sign. Walk past it till you see a canteen and turn left to reach the Connexion lift lobby.
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313449088460525630/IMG_5593.jpg?ex=6750d509&is=674f8389&hm=95222ea1de38167eeeb2c264e23264ea87f5911372d37a46484cb479f89d0f42&=&format=webp&width=1518&height=1138"/>
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1312301293649530940/IMG_5476.jpg?ex=67509c91&is=674f4b11&hm=2533d63696ca59facc66b6535904df14d09d0794bff9e756939811adb37fe08f&=&format=webp&width=1518&height=1138">
        Take the lift to Level 5. You've made it! 
      </p> 
      <h3>
        2.  Bras Basah (Exit B) / Bencoolen (Exit C)
      </h3>
      <p> 
        If you're coming via Bras Basah / Bencoolen, you can get to SMU Connexion via the underground. Walk from the station until you see this large open space.
        Go up the escalator / stairs here.
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313448790795096114/IMG_5588.jpg?ex=6750d4c2&is=674f8342&hm=3880819497f878da2804a5a169840ff0e5ab14ccb533cdedb1e85ad5c89dfa62&=&format=webp&width=1410&height=1058"/>
        Keep going until you reach the end of this corridor.        
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313448791172710462/IMG_5589.jpg?ex=6750d4c2&is=674f8342&hm=1bdffe7f961476fcc0e90f34ee72bfc0a720f769f1ca8a676bfb28318df4f1b4&=&format=webp&width=1410&height=1058"/>
        At the end of the corridor, you should see these doors. The door on the left has stairs to go up, while the door on the right has an escalator. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313448791743008838/IMG_5590.jpg?ex=6750d4c2&is=674f8342&hm=b7726434871468e0b165d891425de8859046b70183835cff84256704c70c4494&=&format=webp&width=1410&height=1058"/>
        Go up to street level and walk towards the canteen. The lift lobby is there. 
        <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1275419865724751924/1313448792967876618/IMG_5476.jpg?ex=6750d4c2&is=674f8342&hm=e41b4b0be1b85fa3a8f34f32174df16e549bbc36da6c56b968efeba6ba735cdc&=&format=webp&width=1410&height=1058"/>
        Take the lift up to Level 5. You've made it! :) 
    </section>
